        {
            "title": "今日我咁睇｜伊朗揚言封海峽 市場反應已減少 港股調整後料再上｜小編苟豪",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"960\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/QXS3R8.PzIdERPTjHA24fQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/bossmind_356/e101e6fc865af363a810b3b9bd821b9e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">1.雖然一直講會悶，不過講市都離不開提及伊朗局勢，昨日伊朗領導人表示要讓海峽停運，油價應聲向上，但升幅相當克制，估計市場亦預期伊朗封鎖對自己的成本亦太高，並不划算，封鎖主要是姿態而非行動。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2.正如昨日所言，油價可能在80至100元反覆上落，現時接近預期的油價高位，可以考慮小注買一注與油價反向的板塊，例如航空股或者指數股，等油價回調後再改買高油價受惠股如石油股、油服股等。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3. 近兩日港股調整，科網股如騰訊及阿里巴巴都相對硬淨，與OpenClaw自然有關。雖然傳出有一批用家因為成本高而不用，但相信仍是未來發展的趨勢，亦是AI應用賺錢的主要途徑之一，對科網股仍是正面影響的因素。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d296f95a-85b9-3c61-a80a-c3622e43f278-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">4. 港股預計在25500點徘徊，下個支持位在25200點，短期有望收復25800點及26000點，若跌至25200點是入貨機會。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">5. 恒指牛熊證街貨比例，牛證街貨回升至六成以上，相反理論暫時不算好，不支持大市大幅向上。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E6%88%91%E5%92%81%E7%9D%87-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E6%8F%9A%E8%A8%80%E5%B0%81%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%8F%8D%E6%87%89%E5%B7%B2%E6%B8%9B%E5%B0%91-%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E5%BE%8C%E6%96%99%E5%86%8D%E4%B8%8A-%E5%B0%8F%E7%B7%A8%E8%8B%9F%E8%B1%AA-020000167.html",
